description: Welcome to the USA Culture Basics course presented by Translate Nursing LLC. Why would you need to learn about the USA Culture?This course is not for those who already frequently visit the USA or those who already live in this country, however, this class is for those who are going to visit this country for the first time or are planning on moving here in the future to work within this country. This course is designed specifically for these people with easier to read terminology and more basic definitions on the information presented. This class is a presentation type of class with a mixture of mash-up videos, presentations, examples and stories and ultimately hand-out materials to help you remember what was covered easier.
title: USA Culture Basics for Traveling Healthcare Professionals
